As you expected, &quot;1984-00&quot; cannot be parsed as a YearMonth.  But you passed `YearMonth::from, Year::from` as your TemporalQuerys, so after parseBest discovers that the string cannot be parsed using YearMonth.from, it tries again using Year.from, which succeeds.

